It is calling pTimeOfDay->Update(true, true);

I think the new TOD system needs pTimeOfDay->LoadPreset(pathAndfileName);

This works for me at least.

In 5.1 if you try to load a save by name, it doesnt pass the ".csf" extension with the fileName.  Loadlastsave does work from the console though.  I didn't try 5.3 yet.

To reproduce just load a map, type in "save name" then "load name".

I added this code to the top and replaced fileName variable with saveGame further down.  It's working so far.
`	string	saveGame = pFileName;
	size_t	pos = saveGame.find(".csf");
	if (pos == string::npos)
	{
		saveGame = saveGame.append(".csf");
	}`
